{"title":"计算面积2（子程序入门）","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":31,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-3282","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>如果一个圆的半径为r，则该圆的面积为π*r*r，其中π表示圆周率。现在有大小不同的三个圆（两个小圆必定在大圆内部，且两个小圆不会相交），半径分别为r1和r2、r3，且大圆半径r1始终大于r2和r3。编程计算大圆中挖掉两个小圆后剩余的面积（即下图所示蓝色区域的面积）。说明：π在本题中取值为3。</p>\n\n<img src=\"/source/codevs/codevs-3282/img/aHR0cDovL3d3dy5qb3lvaS5jbi9wcm9ibGVtL2NvZGV2cy0zMjgyL2h0dHA6Ly9jb2RldnMuY24vbWVkaWEvaW1hZ2UvcHJvYmxlbS8zMjgyLkpQRw==.JPG\" style=\"max-width:700px\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>输入只有一行三个整数r1、r2和r3（0&lt;r2,r3&lt;r1&lt;=50），两个整数之间用 一个空格分隔。第一个整数r1为大圆半径。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>输出只有一行一个整数，表示剩余部分的面积。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>2 1 1</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>6</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>半径不超过50</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}